IBS with Constipation
The recommended dosage of ZelnormÂ® (tegaserod maleate) is 6 mg taken twice daily orally before meals for 4 to 6 weeks. For those women who respond to therapy at 4-6 weeks, an additional 4-6 week course can be considered. 
Chronic Idiopathic Constipation
The recommended dosage of Zelnorm (tegaserod maleate)  is 6 mg taken twice daily orally before meals. Physicians and patients should periodically assess the need for continued therapy. 
